          <h1 id="githubvsgitlabidevscodestudentnotes">GitHub vs GitLab, IDE &amp; VS Code - Student Notes</h1>
<h2 id="tableofcontents">📚 Table of Contents</h2>
<ol>
<li>GitHub vs GitLab</li>
<li>GitLab CE vs GitLab EE</li>
<li>Merging Branches in GitLab</li>
<li>Resolving Conflicts</li>
