</ol>
<hr />
<h2 id="1githubvsgitlab">1️⃣ GitHub vs GitLab</h2>
<h3 id="whataregithubandgitlab"><strong>What are GitHub and GitLab?</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Definition</strong>: 
Both <strong>GitHub</strong> and <strong>GitLab</strong> are web-based platforms that provide Git repository hosting, collaboration tools, and DevOps capabilities. They serve similar purposes but with different features and philosophies.</p>
<h3 id="simpleanalogy"><strong>Simple Analogy</strong> 🏢</h3>
<pre><code>Think of them as Office Buildings:

GitHub:
├─ Like WeWork (shared office space)
├─ Everyone uses the same building
├─ Managed by landlord (Microsoft)
└─ Great for networking

GitLab:
├─ Like owning your building
├─ Can customize everything
├─ Self-managed or cloud
└─ Complete control
</code></pre>
<hr />
<h3 id="detailedcomparison"><strong>Detailed Comparison</strong></h3>
<pre><code>┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              GITHUB vs GITLAB COMPARISON                    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

ASPECT            │ GITHUB                │ GITLAB
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
OWNERSHIP         │ Microsoft             │ GitLab Inc.
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
DEPLOYMENT        │ Cloud only            │ Cloud + Self-hosted
                  │ github.com            │ gitlab.com or own server
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
MARKET SHARE      │ ~70% (largest)        │ ~20%
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
FOCUS             │ Social coding         │ Complete DevOps
                  │ Community             │ Pipeline automation
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
PRICING           │ Free public repos     │ Free unlimited
                  │ Free private repos    │ public + private
                  │ Team: $4/user/month   │ Premium: $29/user/month
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
CI/CD             │ GitHub Actions        │ Built-in GitLab CI/CD
                  │ (added later)         │ (native from start)
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
REPOSITORY        │ Pull Requests         │ Merge Requests
MODEL             │                       │
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
WIKI              │ Separate wiki tab     │ Integrated wiki
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
ISSUE TRACKING    │ Basic issues          │ Advanced issues
                  │                       │ (weights, epics, boards)
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
CODE REVIEW       │ Excellent             │ Excellent
                  │ Line comments         │ Line + file comments
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
CONTAINER         │ GitHub Packages       │ Container Registry
REGISTRY          │                       │ (built-in)
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
SECURITY          │ Dependabot            │ Security Dashboard
                  │ Code scanning         │ SAST, DAST built-in
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
KUBERNETES        │ Via Actions           │ Native integration
INTEGRATION       │                       │ Auto DevOps
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
PROJECT           │ Projects (basic)      │ Advanced planning
MANAGEMENT        │ GitHub Projects Beta  │ Epics, Milestones, Boards
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
IMPORT/EXPORT     │ Limited               │ Full project export
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
SELF-HOSTING      │ ❌ No                 │ ✅ Yes (CE &amp; EE)
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
OPEN SOURCE       │ Platform: ❌          │ Platform: ✅ (CE)
                  │ Projects: ✅          │ Projects: ✅
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
API               │ REST, GraphQL         │ REST, GraphQL
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
LEARNING CURVE    │ Easy (simpler)        │ Moderate (more features)
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
COMMUNITY         │ Massive (90M+ users)  │ Growing (30M+ users)
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
MARKETPLACE       │ Large (Actions)       │ Smaller
──────────────────┼───────────────────────┼────────────────────
IDEAL FOR         │ Open source           │ Enterprise DevOps
                  │ Portfolio             │ Complete CI/CD
                  │ Social coding         │ Self-hosted needs
</code></pre>
<hr />
<h3 id="featurecomparison"><strong>Feature Comparison</strong></h3>
<h4 id="repositoryfeatures"><strong>Repository Features</strong></h4>
<pre><code>GITHUB:
───────
✅ Pull Requests (PR)
✅ Code review
✅ Protected branches
✅ Draft PRs
✅ Auto-merge
✅ GitHub Pages (static hosting)
✅ GitHub Gists (code snippets)
✅ Discussions
✅ Sponsors

GITLAB:
───────
✅ Merge Requests (MR)
✅ Code review
✅ Protected branches
✅ Draft MRs
✅ Auto-merge
✅ GitLab Pages (static hosting)
✅ Snippets
✅ Built-in wiki per project
✅ Design management
✅ File locking
</code></pre>
<hr />
<h4 id="cicdfeatures"><strong>CI/CD Features</strong></h4>
<pre><code>GITHUB ACTIONS:
───────────────
├─ YAML-based workflows
├─ Matrix builds
├─ Reusable workflows
├─ 2,000 free minutes/month (public)
├─ Large marketplace
└─ Integrated with GitHub ecosystem

GITLAB CI/CD:
─────────────
├─ .gitlab-ci.yml
├─ Auto DevOps (automatic pipeline)
├─ Pipeline visualization
├─ 400 free minutes/month (SaaS)
├─ Unlimited for self-hosted
├─ Multi-project pipelines
├─ Parent-child pipelines
└─ Complete DevOps lifecycle
</code></pre>
<hr />
<h4 id="securityfeatures"><strong>Security Features</strong></h4>
<pre><code>GITHUB:
───────
├─ Dependabot (dependency alerts)
├─ Code scanning
├─ Secret scanning
├─ Security advisories
└─ Require 2FA for organizations

GITLAB:
───────
├─ Dependency scanning
├─ SAST (Static Application Security Testing)
├─ DAST (Dynamic Application Security Testing)
├─ Container scanning
├─ License compliance
├─ Security Dashboard
└─ Vulnerability management
</code></pre>
