<h3 id="choosingtherightedition"><strong>Choosing the Right Edition</strong></h3>
<pre><code>┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                 EDITION SELECTOR                         │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

START WITH CE IF:
─────────────────
✅ Individual developer
✅ Team &lt; 10 people
✅ Budget-conscious
✅ Just need Git + CI/CD
✅ Learning DevOps
✅ Open source project

Example: 3-person startup building MVP


UPGRADE TO PREMIUM IF:
──────────────────────
✅ Team 10-100 people
✅ Multiple projects
✅ Need project planning (epics, roadmaps)
✅ Code ownership important
✅ Disaster recovery needed (Geo)
