Example: 50-person company with 3 development teams


UPGRADE TO ULTIMATE IF:
───────────────────────
✅ Team 100+ people
✅ Regulated industry
✅ Compliance requirements
✅ Need 24/7 support
✅ Advanced security scanning
✅ Portfolio management

