├─ Install on your servers
├─ Complete control
├─ No CI/CD minute limits
├─ Data stays in-house
└─ You manage infrastructure

SaaS (GitLab.com):
├─ Managed by GitLab
├─ No maintenance
├─ Auto-updates
├─ CI/CD minute limits apply
└─ Quick to start
