<hr />
<h2 id="3howtomergerepobranchesingitlab">3️⃣ How to Merge Repo Branches in GitLab</h2>
<h3 id="whatismergingingitlab"><strong>What is Merging in GitLab?</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Definition</strong>: 
Merging in GitLab combines changes from one branch into another using <strong>Merge Requests (MR)</strong>, which is GitLab's equivalent of GitHub Pull Requests.</p>
<hr />
<h3 id="mergerequestworkflow"><strong>Merge Request Workflow</strong></h3>
<pre><code>┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│           GITLAB MERGE REQUEST FLOW                      │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

1. CREATE FEATURE BRANCH
   main → feature/new-login

2. MAKE CHANGES
   Edit files, commit

3. PUSH TO GITLAB
   git push origin feature/new-login

4. CREATE MERGE REQUEST
   Via GitLab UI

5. CODE REVIEW
   Team reviews changes

6. APPROVE
   Reviewers approve

7. MERGE
   Changes merged to main

8. DELETE BRANCH (optional)
   Clean up
</code></pre>
<hr />
<h3 id="method1mergeviagitlabwebui"><strong>Method 1: Merge via GitLab Web UI</strong></h3>
<h4 id="stepbystepcreatingmergerequest"><strong>Step-by-Step: Creating Merge Request</strong></h4>
<pre><code>STEP 1: Push Your Branch
─────────────────────────

# Local work
$ git checkout -b feature/add-dashboard
$ echo "dashboard code" &gt; dashboard.html
$ git add dashboard.html
$ git commit -m "Add dashboard page"
$ git push origin feature/add-dashboard

Enumerating objects: 4, done.
To https://gitlab.com/username/project.git
 * [new branch]      feature/add-dashboard -&gt; feature/add-dashboard


STEP 2: GitLab Shows Banner
────────────────────────────

When you visit GitLab project page:

┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ You pushed to feature/add-dashboard                    │
│                                                        │
│ [Create merge request]                                │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

Click [Create merge request]


STEP 3: Fill MR Form
────────────────────

┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ New Merge Request                                        │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                          │
│ Title:                                                   │
│ Add dashboard page                                       │
│                                                          │
│ Description:                                             │
│ ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│ │ ## What does this MR do?                         │   │
│ │ Adds a new dashboard page for user analytics     │   │
│ │                                                   │   │
│ │ ## Changes                                        │   │
│ │ - Created dashboard.html                          │   │
│ │ - Added charts library                            │   │
│ │ - Implemented data fetching                       │   │
│ │                                                   │   │
│ │ ## Screenshots                                    │   │
