# General
Ctrl/⌘ + P                Quick Open
Ctrl/⌘ + Shift + P        Command Palette
Ctrl/⌘ + B                Toggle Sidebar
Ctrl/⌘ + `                Toggle Terminal

# Git
Ctrl/⌘ + Shift + G        Source Control
Ctrl/⌘ + Enter            Commit
Click branch name         Switch branch

# Editing
Ctrl/⌘ + /                Comment
Alt + ↑/↓                 Move line
Ctrl/⌘ + D                Select occurrence
</code></pre>
